  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n\n![Title](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9ceb6fb6ef6e74a5e02470aba0eacb9b92d6dc2e.png)\n<hr>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/koil\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img src=\"https://github.com/SpiritXIV/koil-online-data/blob/main/content/sys/design/images/koil_api_badge.png?raw=true\" alt=\"koil\" width=\"200px\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/kz6ajy99kX\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img src=\"https://github.com/SpiritXIV/koil-online-data/blob/main/content/sys/design/images/koil_discord_badge.png?raw=true\" alt=\"koil\" width=\"200px\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/spiritxiv/tiers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img src=\"https://github.com/SpiritXIV/koil-online-data/blob/main/content/sys/design/images/koil_support_badge.png?raw=true\" alt=\"koil\" width=\"200px\"/>\n  </a>\n  \n  <br>\n\n  <img src=\"https://github.com/SpiritXIV/koil-online-data/blob/main/content/sys/design/images/unfinished_badge.png?raw=true\" alt=\"koil\" width=\"500px\"/>\n</div>\n<hr>\n\nAdds a gameboy and a gameboy color that allow you to play games inside the game!\n![ingame](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9adfd49eeefb022aa7c1c845fa03dd50fcffe625.png)\n\nAnd this is some of the items that are added...\n\n![image](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f7cbc30eb4bb900c73e3f44688a9436d4deee1c9.png)\n\nHow To Video:\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/tTzsi-YvuzU\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\nYou can find gameboy cartradges inside of dungeon chest, strongholds, and more chests.",
